574
00:48:03,600 --> 00:48:05,030
Jo.

575
00:48:06,610 --> 00:48:08,680
Omlouvám se, omlouvám se.

576
00:48:09,780 --> 00:48:12,500
-Jste v pořádku?
-Ano.

577
00:48:40,700 --> 00:48:42,140
<i>Vylez.</i>

578
